- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also likely as the paper discusses communication and data transfer between cloud VMs. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper proposes a methodology for benchmarking and optimizing application performance. 
- cs.Distributed is another possible category as the paper deals with distributed computing on the cloud. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may discuss programming languages used for cloud deployment and optimization.
